  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nUser requested a Chrome extension for comparing Amazon products with a CleanMyMac-inspired interface. Manus created a complete extension with automatic product detection, manual selection, comprehensive comparison features, and a beautiful gradient-based UI. The extension includes full Amazon multi-region support and privacy-focused local data storage.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nUser wanted a practical e-commerce tool for Amazon product comparison with specific design requirements inspired by CleanMyMac's aesthetic\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nDeveloped a complete Chrome extension with automatic product scanning, manual selection capabilities, comprehensive product information extraction, and a polished UI with gradients, animations, and card-based layout\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [Chrome Extension] Amazon Product Comparator — Complete extension package with manifest, popup interface, content scripts, styling, and documentation\n- [Documentation] Installation and Usage Guides — Comprehensive README, installation guide, and quick start documentation\n- [UI Design] CleanMyMac-inspired Interface — Beautiful popup design with gradients, animations, and modern styling\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Target Amazon specifically for better product extraction\n- Use Manifest V3 for Chrome extension compliance\n- Implement both automatic and manual product selection\n- Apply CleanMyMac design language with gradients and animations\n- Store data locally for privacy\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Clear requirements gathering through structured questions\n- Complete package delivery with all necessary files\n- Beautiful UI implementation matching design inspiration\nDiscoveries:\n\n- Extension includes multi-region Amazon support\n- Privacy-focused approach with local data storage\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- Install and test the extension\n- Potentially expand to other e-commerce sites\n- Add more comparison criteria if needed\n---\nUID: o3TMMg2q5ftcp5PzZHZ8UV | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0144\n"
}